<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Greetings. for all of you who don't know most of the illusion spells are available in your enchanter guild no matter what town.However several of the illusions are not found in any but 1 placeErudin has the elemental illusions skeleton illusion & werewolf illusion.You can also find the half elf & halfling illsuion either there or in Qeynos. Can't remember right now which.<p>

    The race issue is up to you.you'll find if you go by stats & want INT you will want an Erudite.if you want fast leveling you'll go w/ a straight human.Want to see at night & have the best CHA,3rd best INT & best WIS then go w/ a high elf . you don't like high elves you say.Well that is why when you see me walking around I look like a woodelf or a fire ele. We have illusions so can be whatever we want.Personally high elves are the best choice...<p>

Mazrim Taim Ma'Hael<br>
